fm: int minSizeSubarray(vector<int>& nums, int target)      {         LL total  = accumulate(nums.begin(), nums.end(), 0LL);          int n = nums.size();         for (int i=0; i<n; i++)             nums.push_back(nums[i]);          vector<LL>presum(2*n, 0);         presum[0] = nums[0];         for (int i=1; i<2*n; i++)             presum[i] = presum[i-1] +  nums[i];          LL ret = INT_MAX/2;          unordered_map<LL, int>Map; // presum module, index         Map[0] = -1;         for (int i=0; i<2*n; i++)         {             LL r = ((presum[i] - target) % total + total) % total;              if (Map.find(r)!=Map.end())             {                 int j = Map[r];                 LL k = ((j==-1? 0: presum[j]) - presum[i] + target) / total;                 ret = min(ret, i-j+k*n);             }              Map[presum[i]%total] = i;         }          if (ret == INT_MAX/2) return -1;         else return ret;             }
